title: Welcome to Hollywood! Please Temper Your Expectations
summary: Once a global magnet for star-struck tourists, Hollywood is now struggling to fill its own sidewalks — even the Walk of Fame is having trouble drawing a crowd.

title: Top 10 trending destinations for U.S. travelers in 2026: 'Americans are discovering their own backyard,' expert says
